headline: lululemon athletica inc. Announces First Quarter Fiscal 2025 Earnings Conference Call
summary: VANCOUVER, British Columbia, May 22, 2025--lululemon athletica inc. (NASDAQ: LULU) today announced that its financial results for the first quarter fiscal 2025 will be released Thursday, June 5, 2025. The company will host a conference call at 4:30 p.m. Eastern time to discuss the financial results.
